select `c`.`companyname`, `c`.`address`, `co`.`customer_id`, `co`.`sr_no`, `co`.`date` as `order_date`, `order_items`.*, `i`.`name` as `item_name`, `m`.`name` as `marka_name`, `m`.*, (SELECT SUM(oi.quantity) FROM order_items as oi WHERE oi.deleted_at is null and oi.vakkal_number = order_items.vakkal_number and oi.item_id=order_items.item_id and oi.sort <= order_items.sort and oi.type='inward') AS total_inward, (SELECT SUM(oi.quantity) FROM order_items as oi WHERE oi.deleted_at is null and oi.vakkal_number = order_items.vakkal_number and oi.item_id=order_items.item_id and oi.sort <= order_items.sort and oi.type='outward') AS total_outward, (SELECT SUM(IF(oi.type='inward',oi.quantity*oi.weight,0))-SUM(IF(oi.type='outward',oi.quantity*oi.weight,0)) FROM order_items as oi WHERE oi.deleted_at is null and oi.vakkal_number = order_items.vakkal_number and oi.item_id=order_items.item_id and oi.sort <= order_items.sort) AS total_balance_weight from `order_items` left join `customer_orders` as `co` on `co`.`customer_order_id` = `order_items`.`customer_order_id` left join `customers` as `c` on `co`.`customer_id` = `c`.`customer_id` left join `items` as `i` on `i`.`item_id` = `order_items`.`item_id` left join `marka` as `m` on `m`.`marka_id` = `order_items`.`marka_id` where `order_items`.`deleted_at` is null and `co`.`customer_id` = '12' and `order_items`.`deleted_at` is null order by `c`.`companyname` asc, `i`.`name` asc, `vakkal_number` asc, `order_items`.`sort` asc
